snippet.title: Extreme Corseter Shrinks Waist From 38 to 23 Inches

localized.description:
Extreme Corseter Shrinks Waist From 38 to 23 Inches

SUBSCRIBE: http://bit.ly/Oc61Hj

MOST women dream of having an hourglass figure -- but Penny Brown has taken it to extraordinary new levels. In the last two years, she has undergone two breast implant surgeries -- taking her from an H to an O cup. And she has shrunk her waist from 38 to just 23 inches by squeezing herself into a tiny corset -- sometimes for up to 23 hours a day. This has resulted in the 25-year-old's bust being TWICE the size of her waist! Disturbingly, the corset can be so tight that when Australian-born Penny is wearing them she can only eat smaller meals -- because her stomach is so restricted. Bending, sitting and lying down can also be problematic and doing exercise or sports is completely off limits because she'd struggle to breathe properly. But, despite it all Penny, who lives in Okinawa, Japan, believes it's all worth it.

Videographer / Director: Aflo
Producer: Emma Pearson 
Editor: Joshua Douglas
